Barroso Says EU Should Accelerate Start of Permanent Rescue Fund

-- B y   J o n a t h a n   S t e a r n s
-- 
2011-09-28T07:19:09Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-28/barroso-says-eu-should-accelerate-start-of-permanent-rescue-fund.html
European Commission President  Jose
Barroso  said the European Union should accelerate the start-up
of its permanent bailout fund, the  European Stability
Mechanism. He spoke today to the European Parliament in
Strasbourg,  France .  To contact the reporter on this story:
Jonathan Stearns in Strasbourg at 
 jstearns2@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
